'''''P.I.''''' sometimes referred to as '''''Private Investigator''''' is a Singaporean crime/thriller drama starring [[Carl Ng]], Vanessa Vanderstraaten, [[Karylle]], Kathiravan Kandavelu, Joyce Ng, Najib Soiman and Shane Mardjuki.

The series premiered on MediaCorp TV Channel 5 on January 9, 2017.<ref name=Birthdate>{{cite web|url=http://tv.toggle.sg/en/channel5/shows/p-i-tif/info|title=P.I. (TIF) Show Info|publisher=Toggle|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106015628/http://tv.toggle.sg/en/channel5/shows/p-i-tif/info|archivedate=2017-01-06|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=P.I.|url=http://tv.toggle.sg/en/shows/p-i-tif/info|publisher=Toggle|accessdate=23 June 2017}}</ref>

